---+++ [[ArgumentMining/ArgumentationSchemes][Argumentation models]] (Wiki)
   * Walton, Reed, Macagno, 2008
      * also: re-read introduction
   * The use of argument (Toulmin 1958) 
      * considered as the first work on argumentative structures
