      * scientific domain
      * also: CARS - Creating a research space (Swales 1990) 
      * also: Extension to CARS (Teufel, Carletta, Moens, at EACL 1999)
   * Workshop on Discourse Connectors 
      * -> great overview of work around discourse connectives
