---+++ From Wiki (Newspaper)
   * ?Using Argumentation Schemes for Argument Extraction: A Bottom-Up Method (Walton, 2012) IGI Global
      * focuses on Walton's argumentation schemes; tries to cluster schemes by similarity...
      * "It was found that 37.1% of the arguments collected did not fit any of the fourteen schemes" 
